<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <%- include("../partials/head") %>

</head>

<body>

<%- include("../partials/navbar") %>

<!-- ==================================
429 Error
================================== -->

<section class="py-5">

<div class="container">

<div class="row justify-content-center">

<div class="col-lg-8 text-center">

<div class="mb-4">

<i
class="fa-solid fa-hourglass-half text-warning"
style="font-size:100px;"></i>

</div>

<h1
class="display-1 fw-bold text-warning">

429

</h1>

<h2 class="fw-bold">

Too Many Requests

</h2>

<p class="lead text-muted">

You've made too many requests in a short period of time.

Please wait a few minutes before trying again.

</p>

<div class="mt-4">

<a
href="/"
class="btn btn-warning btn-lg me-2">

<i class="fa-solid fa-house me-2"></i>

Go Home

</a>

<button
onclick="history.back()"
class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">

<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>

Go Back

</button>

</div>

<hr class="my-5">

<h4 class="fw-bold">

Why am I seeing this?

</h4>

<p class="text-muted">

This website uses rate limiting to protect against spam,
abuse and automated requests. If you continue browsing
normally, access will be restored automatically after a
short waiting period.

</p>

<div class="row mt-5">

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved fa-2x text-success mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Secure

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Protects our servers from abuse.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-clock fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Wait

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Try again after a few minutes.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="col-md-4">

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">

<div class="card-body">

<i class="fa-solid fa-headset fa-2x text-danger mb-3"></i>

<h5>

Support

</h5>

<p class="text-muted mb-0">

Contact us if the issue continues.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- ==================================
Need Help?
================================== -->

<section class="py-5 bg-light">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">

            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">

                    Still Seeing This Error?

                </h2>

                <p class="text-muted">

                    If you're still receiving this message after waiting for a
                    few minutes, please contact our support team. We'll be
                    happy to help resolve the issue.

                </p>

                <div class="mt-4">

                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="btn btn-primary me-2">

                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope me-2"></i>

                        Contact Support

                    </a>

                    <a
                        href="/"
                        class="btn btn-outline-dark">

                        <i class="fa-solid fa-house me-2"></i>

                        Back to Home

                    </a>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- ==================================
Footer
================================== -->

<%- include("../partials/footer") %>

<!-- ==================================
Scripts
================================== -->

<%- include("../partials/scripts") %>

</body>

</html>
